---
title: Beef Meatballs in Cannellini Bean Stew with DIY pan con tomate
description: These juicy meatballs simmered in cannellini bean stew are inspired by the traditional Spanish dish 'albóndigas' which are a type of meatball. Another Iberian staple included in this meal is the iconic Catalan tapa 'pan con tomate'.
